data.summary: CodinClub Orientation Powered By BridgeLabz!! By Kanchan
data.description:
Hi,

Congrats!! After going through a screening process we are happy to tell you that we are offering you to join our CodInClub Program. 

You are required to attend our online orientation, where we will explain the whole CodInClub process.

On account of current environmental challenges- coronavirus and an economic slowdown have severely hit the job market. Finding a new job in a recession will be a massive challenge and hence you need a battle plan.

BridgeLabz is launching CodInClub for deserving engineers like you.  After all, your dream job doesn’t just exist. You have to create it, and we at BridgeLabz are committed to helping you in finding the path to your dreams.

 BridgeLabz successfully placed over 1300+ engineers in 250+ companies till date.

 Don’t miss this opportunity amidst this severe employability crisis!!

How to join the orientation?

1. To join using a web browser (laptop), click on meet.google.com/cna-ciic-bbx(click on this link to join the call on 11th June 2020 at 1 pm)

2. To join using a mobile phone: Download Hangouts Meet app and then click   on meet.google.com/cna-ciic-bbx(click on this link to join the call on 11th June 2020 at 1 pm)

 Regards,

Team BridgeLabz

data.description:
Hi,

Congrats!! After going through a screening process we are happy to tell you that we are offering you to join our CodInClub Program. 

You are required to attend our online orientation, where we will explain how you will get your dream job!  

On account of current environmental challenges- coronavirus and an economic slowdown have severely hit the job market. Finding a new job in a recession will be a massive challenge and hence you need a battle plan.

BridgeLabz is launching CodInClub for deserving engineers like you.  After all, your dream job doesn’t just exist. You have to create it, and we at BridgeLabz are committed to helping you in finding the path to your dreams.

 BridgeLabz successfully placed over 1300+ engineers in 250+ companies till date.

 Don’t miss this opportunity amidst this severe employability crisis!! Get your DREAM JOB!!
